name: Lueed
description:
Lueed lives on the ground of the sea; watches glowing jellyfish swim by gazing at mystery.

Lueed wears a pink fleece hoodie with an official Kwerks® emblem.

The stuffing is 100% polyester off-cut PolarGuard™,  that is moisture and rot resistant, easily laundered and non-allergenic.

Approximately 23" High x 19" Wide x 4" Deep

name: Whirb
description:
Whirb hanging in the shade off a sturdy branch, enjoying the warm winds swifting through the ranch.

Whirb wears a burnt orange ultra-suede jacket with an official Kwerks® emblem.

The stuffing is 100% polyester off-cut PolarGuard™,  that is moisture and rot resistant, easily laundered and non-allergenic.

Approximately 18" High x 31" Wide x 5" Deep

name: Thano
description:
Thano shines in a coat of maroon, playing and laughing singing the same tune.

Thano wears a maroon heavy weight jacket in upholstery fabric with an official Kwerks® emblem.

The stuffing is 100% polyester off-cut PolarGuard™,  that is moisture and rot resistant, easily laundered and non-allergenic.

Approximately 25" High x 23" Wide x 5" Deep

name: Drope
description:
Drope swings in a loop off the moon, creating a spiral down landing on a triangle sand dune.

Drope wears dark teal cotton-velvet sweater with an official Kwerks® emblem. 

The stuffing is 100% polyester off-cut PolarGuard™,  that is moisture and rot resistant, easily laundered and non-allergenic.

Approximately 23" High x 23" Wide x 8" Deep

name: Set of 9
description:
The set of 9 Kwerks include:
Thano, Whirb, Dulf, Irea, Lueed, Jeco, Drope, Zuki, and Baloog
